			button(type="button" data-micromodal-iframe='http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8LPVOjjSgDE' data-micromodal-open='video-modal').video-link._fit
					img._fit-img(src="img/page-menu/video-cover.jpg" alt="alt")
					span.play-icon
						img(src="img/play.svg" alt="alt")
		
		section.ld-text-block
			.wrapper
				h2.ld-title Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit.
				p.ld-text Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus Donec quam felis, ultricies nec
